records.Key Findings:
Technologies and innovations should be consistent with circumstances, objectives and the preferences of farmers;
Extension services play a pivotal role in technology transfer to bridge the gap between research and farmers;
Adaptive research is necessary to assess suitability of technologies to farmers environments; and
Experiential training approaches, such as FFBS, encourage adoption of technologies.

